:name: Mi-V
:description: This script runs AzureRTOS sample on a Mi-V RISC-V board.

$name?="Mi-V"

using sysbus
mach create $name
machine LoadPlatformDescription @platforms/boards/miv-board.repl

showAnalyzer uart

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF  @build/sample_threadx.elf
"""
runMacro $reset
machine StartGdbServer 3333
